        &lt;h2 id=&#34;requirements&#34;&gt;Requirements&lt;/h2&gt;


&lt;div class=&#34;pageinfo pageinfo-primary&#34;&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Choose a suitable overarching design.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Enforce system-wide consistency with domain-driven design.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Define components.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;/div&gt;

